        <inlineHelpText>Enter a specific Campaign Member status to use when NPPatch links the Primary Contact to the Campaign. Leave blank to use the default (responded for Closed/Won, non-responded otherwise).</inlineHelpText>
        <label>Primary Contact Campaign Member Status</label>
